{"tid":897454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【換政務司長？】張建宗：特首已說沒這件事　不再補充","createTime":"2018-11-11T02:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T02:17:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf0ee5c8762bf1874b7472b678e6701e974ac2f","tid":897454,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"有報道指，特首林鄭月娥有意向中央表達撤換政務司長張建宗。結束瑞士訪問行程昨日返港的張建宗表示，「特首在今早（昨早）已經很清楚地再度回應，是沒有這件事。我不再補充任何事。多謝你們。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥昨早回應事件時稱，「完全沒有這件事」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181111/s00001/1541895231277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181111%2Fs00001%2F1541895231277&d=w5dhjXZP8%2BCC%2Ft1jVEv2cP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=13ba4cba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181111%2Fs00001%2F1541895231277&h=fb17b5ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181111/s00001/1541895231277</a>"},{"pid":"4a026d2cca67662b40e916b278f1ced7fffe9bee","tid":897454,"uid":8439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭最初都話無打算選CE"}]}